{"list":[{"title":"目的","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">研究电容器两极板间电势差跟所带电荷量的关系。</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"原理","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><em><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">C=Q/U</span></span></em><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">。</span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"器材","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">电源、开关、双掷开关、规格相同电容器</span>2<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个、电压表</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"步骤","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">1.按电路图连接电路；</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">2.双掷开关</span>S1<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">接</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，给电容器</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">A</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">充电；</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">3.双掷开关</span>S1<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">接</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，观察电压表示数变化；</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">4.断开</span>S1<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，闭合开关</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">S2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，让电容器</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">B</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">放电；</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">5.断开</span>S2<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">S1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">接</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，观察电压表示数变化；</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">6.重复操作步骤</span>4<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，观察电压表示数变化。</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"结论","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">电容器的电荷量变为原来的一半时，其两极板间的电势差也变为原来的一半。</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"补充","data":"<p><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><em><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">C=Q/U</span></span></em><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">。</span></span></span></p>"}],"x":0,"y":0,"width":600,"height":600}